0:00:01,00 --> 0:00:08,00
Website with a nice bootstrap4 support (use of components: navbar + nav + jumbotron + cards + alerts +  ).

2
0:00:08,00 --> 0:00:26,00
User can register with username and password, a flash msg with category success or danger shows the results.

3
0:00:27,00 --> 0:00:37,00
User can login using its credentials. He is redirected to a search webpage.

4
0:00:38,00 --> 0:00:48,00
A multi-criteria search is available using ISBN, title and author. User can type a partial part of ISBN and the search will consider all available ISBNs with the searched term.

5
0:00:49,00 --> 0:01:05,00
A search by partial part of the title is also available. A search by author name is also possible. 

6
0:01:06,00 --> 0:01:12,00
A click on the link of a card for a specific book leads to a more detailed webpage with rating 0 to 5.

7
0:01:13,00 --> 0:01:18,00
The webapp uses the Goodrads api to retrieve some data: such as avg ratings and number of rating of the current book.

8
0:01:19,00 --> 0:01:38,00
A possibility to submit and save a comment review with a note for any book in the db. And the comment and the note persist.

